---
// No props needed
---

<section class="resume-section scroll-reveal-animate">
  <h2>Master's Capstone Project</h2>
  <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"
        ><strong
          >Identifying Disadvantaged Communities Using Cumulative Environmental
          Burden</strong
        ></span
      >
      <span class="date">January 2025 – June 2025</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        <strong>Role:</strong> Lead Data Analyst and Developer &emsp; <wbr />
        <strong>Client:</strong> Dr. Jayajit Chakraborty
      </li>
      <li>
        Conducted spatial statistical analysis to identify areas of high
        cumulative environmental burden using over 30 environmental and
        socio-economic indicators.
      </li>
      <li>
        Improved existing geospatial mapping tool to visualize new results,
        including back-end data pipeline modification in Python and front-end
        client navigation in TypeScript and React.
        <ul>
          <li>
            Application: <a
              href="https://apps.bren.ucsb.edu/justice40"
              target="_blank">apps.bren.ucsb.edu/justice40</a
            >.
          </li>
          <li>
            GitHub Repository: <a
              href="https://github.com/Justice40-MEDS"
              target="_blank">github.com/Justice40-MEDS</a
            >.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .resume-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 2.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--text-muted);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  ul {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }
  .project-entry {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem; /* Space between entries */
  }
  .project-entry:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .project-entry .header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .project-entry .date {
    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .project-entry .details {
    list-style: disc; /* Use bullet points */
    padding-left: 1.5rem; /* Standard padding for list */
    margin-left: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .project-entry .details li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .project-entry p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .project-entry .header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .project-entry .date {
      margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }
  }

  .more-projects-link {
    margin-top: 3rem; /* Add space above this line */
    font-size: 1.2 rem;
  }
</style>
